  "detailed_description": "<h1>Attending Mass</h1><p>Our Ball, Who art in Steam, \r\nJust Roll With It be Thy Name. \r\nThy Vidya come. \r\nThy Achievements be done, \r\non Japanese Level as it is in Haunted House.\r\n\r\nGive us this day our daily fun. \r\nAnd forgive us our exploits, \r\nas we forgive those who glitch against us. \r\nAnd lead us not into micro-transactions, \r\nbut deliver us from boredom. Amen.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>\"Just Roll With It\" is an action platforming roller ball game with light puzzle elements. The game has multiple levels of varying difficulty and themes. From an ocean docks to a child's playroom or ancient temple setting there is a lot of variety in scenery.",
